---
description: Card UI for dashboard and proposal blocks
globs: ["src/components/**/*Card.tsx", "src/pages/**/*Card.tsx"]
alwaysApply: true
---

- Use `rounded-xl`, `shadow-sm`, `p-4`, and `bg-white` as the card base.
- Maintain vertical spacing with `space-y-2` or `space-y-4` depending on content density.
- Use `flex flex-col` or `grid` layout for structured internal sections.
- Apply `text-base text-gray-700` for body content, and `font-semibold text-lg` for titles.
- For dashboard metric cards, include `text-sm uppercase text-muted` labels.
- Avoid hardcoded pixel values; use Tailwind spacing tokens (`p-4`, `gap-6`, etc.).
